c=[]
for i in fifa.Value:
    if i[-1]=='M':
            m = float(i[1:-1])
            f = m*1000000
            c.append(f)
    elif i[-1]=='K':
            k = float(i[1:-1])
            j = k*1000
            c.append(j)
    else:
        j=float(i[1:])
        c.append(j)

m=np.array(c)
fifa.Value=m

c=[]
for i in fifa['Release Clause']:
    if isinstance(i,float)==False:
        if i[-1]=='M':
            m = float(i[1:-1])
            f = m*1000000
            c.append(f)
        elif i[-1]=='K':
            k = float(i[1:-1])
            j = k*1000
            c.append(j)
        else:
            j=float(i[1:])
            c.append(j)
    else:
        c.append(i)
m=np.array(c)
fifa['Release Clause']=m
